{"tid":2154807,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國水利部：大水之年是豐收年　不影響糧食供應","createTime":"2020-08-13T10:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T14:28:08.000Z","uid":241764,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"54384c092eed2fa3976240854f8011db1ba86ecf","tid":2154807,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:36:09.000Z","msg":"內地汛期持續，至今共有超過六千萬人受災。當局預期，汛期會延長到九月底，強調大水之年是豐收年，不會影響糧食供應，會繼續嚴防死守救災。<br />\n<br />\n內地長江、淮河流域自六月以來，發生嚴重汛情，降雨量達759.2毫米，持續62日，是自1961年以來最多及持續最長時間。全國有634條河流發生超警以上洪水，長江部分河段、洞庭湖、鄱陽湖及太湖水位仍處於超警狀態。<br />\n<br />\n洪災共造成6346萬人受災，219人死亡和消失，五萬四千套房屋倒塌，直接經濟損失近一千八百億元，比過去五年平均水平多出超過一成。當局緊急轉移安置超過400萬人，當局強調，洪災不會影響國家糧食供應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401589\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401589&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzhqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=36541299\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401589&h=2cc46e00\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401589</a>"},{"pid":"a04520d9db10246e35fb63060f3b5edfb6049f79","tid":2154807,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:36:38.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzhqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=2dfd97be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"},{"pid":"92e39cb2095fe6e84ffe807b24719292d8c2eb7d","tid":2154807,"uid":282569,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"唔講由自可 <br />\n佢ㄧ講 真係令人放心曬"},{"pid":"d704c4e800f884d3988320712